using System.IO;

File----file working
FileInfo-------------------------info on file======Instance Methods
Directory-----folders working ----Directory is a static class with static methods
DirectoryInfo-----------info on folders/directory============Instance Methods


text, binary,xml,json---------FileStream=====instance methods ====creating file, giving access to the file,setting the mode of the file

FileMode: Create,CreateNew,Append,Truncate,Open,OpenOrCreate
FileAccess: Read, Write, ReadWrite

StreamReader: read from the file
StreamWriter: write to the file
